'''Cocoricò''' is a [[nightclub]] in [[Riccione]], [[Province of Rimini]], [[Italy]]. Open since 1989, it has become Italy's largest and most renowned dance venue; [[DJ Mag]] ranks it at 25th place in its 2016 World Top 100 clubs list. It can accommodate up to 6,000 people.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://djmag.com/top100clubs | title=Top 100 Clubs | publisher=djmag.com | accessdate=8 May 2016}}</ref>

