'''Hauteclere''' (or Halteclere, or Hauteclaire, literally "High and neat") is the [[sword]] of [[Olivier (The Song of Roland)|Olivier]], a character in the medieval French epic ''[[The Song of Roland]]''. It is described as being of burnished [[steel]], with a [[crystal]] embedded in a [[gold]]en [[hilt]].

== In Popular Culture ==
In the video game series [[Fire Emblem]] Hauteclere is the name of an axe wielded by the character Princess Minerva.
The anime, light novel, and manga series [[High School DxD]], also includes Hauteclere as a holy sword wielded by shidou irina.{{Notable swords}}
